cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.RO 

This paper focuses on video representation and reasoning, which involves computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The evaluation of computational models on a wide range of reasoning tasks suggests that machine learning (cs.LG) and natural language processing (cs.CL) are also relevant sub-categories. Additionally, the study of causal relations in videos may involve robotics (cs.RO) applications.
